{
  "stem": "833.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For three or four months, he couldn't wear one shoe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a man, a Jew, who was an informant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, that's not right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's wrong.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody wanted to kill him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- the SS wanted to kill him, because he-- he-- he informed on the SS.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was his stupidity.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a Viennese lawyer who didn't want to get through that type of work of Dachau and Buchenwald and in the very, very beginning decided to become an informer.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we knew it very soon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had to stay away from him, because he-- it was a great danger to talk to him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No, he-- he went so stupidly to the-- to the SS heads and told them about the business deeds that the SS was doing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they, of course, went immediately back and-- and tried to kill him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's what they did finally.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't say that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was something else.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, he was-- the things-- Jura and I who wanted to get him-- he was heavily, heavily beaten and wounded.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I mean, he was really-- and he became suddenly a human being, asking for his mother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And neither Jura nor I could stand that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we took him on the-- on the stretcher and brought him to the-- the prisoners' hospital.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the prisoners wouldn't-- wouldn't take him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's the story.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They refused.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we put him back to our barrack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There we had to leave him outside on the-- on-- not-- not outside in the outside, but outside of-- of our rooms.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Our-- and that's where he was killed by the SS-- with sand sacks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's a nice way to die.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, you mean the yard stick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The yard stick?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I found that yard stick.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
